  schema:name "Brassicaceae" ;
  schema:description "Mustard/crucifer family — ~372 genera, ~4,060 species. Diagnostic 4-petaled cross-shaped (cruciform) flower, tetradynamous stamens (4 long + 2 short), glucosinolate-myrosinase defense system. Includes cole crops (cabbage, broccoli, kale), spices, and important model organism Arabidopsis." ;
